### CheckPoint — Admin Reports endpoints
### Requires an ADMIN account. See admin-users.http for the login request.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = PASTE_YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_HERE

### List all reports (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/reports?page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List reports filtered by type ("review" or "comment")
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/reports?page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc&type=review
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get a single report by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/reports/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Dismiss (delete) a report
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/reports/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
